    "description": "How can a slime change the world around it? In this incredible <strong>cozy game</strong>, experience the relaxing journey of <strong>cleaning</strong> with acids, automatic <strong>repairs</strong>, and a unique story!<br><br>Slime the Cleaner is a simple game where your goal is to relax and clean everything around you.<br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >How to clean?</h2></strong><br><br>Clean and repair everything around you! Meet the best cleaner in the world: Slime. With various acids available, you can change your own chemistry and appearance to clean even the toughest stains. And if that's not enough, we also have upgrades to choose from! <br><br><strong>Talk to everyone!</strong> Skeletons, golems, giant rats, and much more—all needing your services, each with a story to tell. Will you be able to help them all? <br><br><strong>Explore a world</strong> full of castles, dungeons, hideouts, and more! All in need of immediate cleaning. Watch everything transform with each step you take.<br><br>----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Come visit our Kickstarter Page!</h2><br>Help contribute to our campaign and get the game for $2 now!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3159310/extras/SlimeTheCleanerKick600.png?t=1742758453\" /></span><br><br>",
